# Raj Electronics Ledger — Playwright Tests

Automated test suite for https://electronics-ledger.netlify.app

## Tests
- **Smoke** — checks app loads and key elements are visible
- **API response handling** — tests dashboard with mock data including missing data and rate limit errors
- **Offline banner** — checks offline warning message appears

## Results
7 tests · 7 passed · 0 failed

## How to run
```bash
npm install
npx playwright install
npx playwright test
```

## Tech
Playwright · TypeScript · Chromium
